# UDO Changelog

## v4.4.0 (2025-01-09)

### Modular Architecture
Complete restructure to modular file-based system.

#### New Structure
```
modules/
├── core/           # Core system files
├── templates/      # Agent and document templates
├── rules/          # Default quality standards
└── takeover/       # Optional takeover module
```

#### Benefits
- Edit individual files without regenerating entire installer
- Update single files in GitHub
- Takeover is now `--with-takeover` flag
- Easier to review changes
- Smaller, focused updates

### Layered Rule System
- **HARD_STOPS.md** (Layer 0) - Absolute rules, never override
- **.rules/*.md** (Layer 1) - Detailed standards
- **.agents/*.md** (Layer 2) - Agent-specific rules
- **LESSONS_LEARNED.md** (Layer 3) - Situational lessons

### Enhanced Teaching Protocol
- Correction capture prompts
- Conflict detection
- Layer determination
- Lesson review triggers

### Install Options
```bash
# Standard install
curl -fsSL .../install.sh | bash

# With takeover module
curl -fsSL .../install.sh | bash -s -- --with-takeover
```

## v4.3.1 (2025-01-08)
- Auto-checkpoints
- Circuit breakers
- Memory discipline
- Context janitor
